text:
so after much code working with my team, macro probably is most successful:
```{%- macro getContentType(tagsArray) -%}
    {% set contentTypeTag = {"tag":"Blog"} %}
    {%- for tag in tagsArray -%} 
        {% set tagName = tag|string %}
        {%- if tagName is string_containing  "Content Type " -%}  
            {% do contentTypeTag.update({"tag": tagName|replace('Content Type ','')}) %}
        {%- endif -%}
    {%- endfor -%}
    {{contentTypeTag.tag}}
{%- endmacro -%}```
